name: 36 Days of Type || M // Magneto (13/36)
description: From his Wiki: Magneto is a powerful mutant who has the ability to generate and control magnetic fields. Magneto regards mutants as evolutionarily superior to humans and rejects the possibility of peaceful human-mutant coexistence; he initially aimed to conquer the world to enable mutants, whom he refers to as homo superior, to replace humans as the dominant species. The typeface used for Magneto is Agency FB, Bold.
